Author: lyssland
Text: it gives me like a very small glimmer of hope that occasionally i have days that i think i look good and am happy to wear most clothing and i feel like i even get more compliments on those days from others  however... usually i can't wear most of my clothes without freaking out and have very specific rules (must wear large cardigan every day at work so no one will ever see the true shape of my body or my protruding belly or my weird significant weight loss despite never being overweight!)

Author: LightheadedFairy
Text: Omg, I am the exact same way, I thought I was the only one...
